<p>
	This is a fantastic festive take on the traditional set of three see no evil, hear no evil, speak no evil. This lovely looking ornament would complement any room within a house with a simple festive touch. This decoration is all one piece and consists of three colourful Santas, each illustrating one of the three sayings. They are standing on a cream oval base with a decorative holly design around the outside. This ornament is approximately 15cm tall and 16cm wide.</p>
